Category:  OLC  Topic:  tog_mflag



Used to toggle critter flags, including mob flags.

syntax:  tog_mflag [flag_num] [Crit_flag/Mob_flag] <n_th> [crit name]

example:  tog_mflag 3 mob_flag 2.guard 	Toggles mob_flags # 3
          tog_mflag 5 crit_f 3.citizen 	Toggles 5_th critter flag

Bugs:  Some flags are (and should be) restricted from toggling.  As
       an Imp adds/deletes/changes flags, he/she should check this
       and similar functions for possible tweaking.

See also:  olc, tog_oflag, tog_rflag, mclone, mstat
